{"type": "article", "id": 25703, "title": "用绳索编织出贝壳纹路靠背的椅子", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-20T07:00:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 16, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607165156FRsofvct6mgAka90.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">伦敦的设计工作室 doshi levien 为西班牙家具品牌 kettal 设计了这张椅子，椅子本身有些像贝壳或者一面扇子，有宽大的椅背和低矮的座位，很适合放在户外。在铝制的金属框架中用绳索编织出扶手和靠背，有自然和疏松的感觉。经过光线的照射后，椅背的纹路就会在地上投下像贝壳一样的一圈一圈散开的阴影，对称且优雅。<a href=\"http://www.kettal.com/kettal/blog_post.php?id=3086&amp;tipo=N&amp;IdiomaWeb=CAS\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071651548xZJFhVWMXfAdton.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607165154KZodMlhxQe2cvyaw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607165155N0nwJAWFERIrH42a.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071651555ELhuIeCFc7p3aiN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76528117\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><br></p>\n\n\n"}